    public class HTMLElement
extends Element
    The JavaScript object HTMLElement which is the base class for all HTML objects. This will typically wrap an instance of HtmlElement.
    Author:
    Mike Bowler, David K. Taylor, Barnaby Court, Christian Sell, Chris Erskine, David D. Kilzer, Daniel Gredler, Marc Guillemot, Hans Donner, Bruce Faulkner, Ahmed Ashour, Sudhan Moghe, Ronald Brill, Frank Danek
